    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-8059-82d1-c9fe7d5d41e6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Team formation is one of the most important steps in successful collaborative learning activities. However, it is difficult for a multitude of reasons: talent, knowledge, interactions, etc… The main goal of the paper is to create a theory-driven framework to group formation.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-8059-82d1-c9fe7d5d41e6",
